  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK927">
<l>uḷḷoṟṟi yuḷḷūr nakappaṭuva reññāṉṟuṅ </l>
<l>kaḷḷoṟṟik kaṇcāy pavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who always intoxicate themselves by a private (indulgence in) drink will have their secrets detected and laughed at by their fellow-townsmen.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
